[Ya, tuan.]

789
00:34:12,760 --> 00:34:14,160
[Siapa perempuan itu?]

790
00:34:25,480 --> 00:34:26,280
Kenapa?

791
00:34:27,640 --> 00:34:28,880
Penapis Lai mengadu
di depan Maharani Balu.

792
00:34:28,960 --> 00:34:30,240
[Katanya, Ketua Shen
tidak berusaha dalam siasatan.]

793
00:34:30,360 --> 00:34:31,359
Maharani Balu menurunkan titah

794
00:34:31,359 --> 00:34:32,640
supaya Ketua Shen ditangkap.

795
00:34:37,480 --> 00:34:38,520
Kamu berdua menjaga di depan pintu.

796
00:34:38,520 --> 00:34:39,400
Jika ada berita tentang Ketua Shen,

797
00:34:39,400 --> 00:34:40,080
maklum dengan segera!

798
00:34:40,080 --> 00:34:40,720
Ya, tuan.

799
00:34:42,240 --> 00:34:43,120
Tak boleh masuk.

