00:35:06,200 --> 00:35:07,000
[Tak boleh cari!]

808
00:35:07,120 --> 00:35:08,560
Jika cari lagi, saya ambil tindakan.

809
00:35:10,600 --> 00:35:11,680
Jangan cari lagi!

