00:35:27,880 --> 00:35:28,800
Harap-harap sempat lagi

817
00:35:28,800 --> 00:35:29,840
kita hantar warkah.

818
00:35:56,240 --> 00:35:57,000
[Tak sangka tulisan puan serupa]

819
00:35:57,000 --> 00:35:58,040
[dengan Ketua Shen.]

820
00:36:08,240 --> 00:36:09,040
Adakan puan yakin

821
00:36:09,040 --> 00:36:09,680
cara ini dapat

822
00:36:09,680 --> 00:36:10,480
selamatkan Ketua Shen?

823
00:36:10,480 --> 00:36:12,280
Tidak semestinya
boleh balik dengan selamat,

824
00:36:12,440 --> 00:36:13,760
namun harus kita cuba.

825
00:36:14,160 --> 00:36:15,520
[Mungkin boleh elak daripada hukuman berat.]

826
00:36:27,520 --> 00:36:28,280
Mengapa termenung?

827
00:36:28,280 --> 00:36:29,320
Cepat pergi!

828
00:36:29,880 --> 00:36:31,000
Saya tunggu di rumah.

829
00:36:32,080 --> 00:36:33,200
Jangan puan mencari dengan sesuka hati.

