00:36:44,400 --> 00:36:46,000
Namun, belum lagi ada hasil.

833
00:36:46,320 --> 00:36:48,200
[Kini, khabar angin disebar luas.]

834
00:36:48,400 --> 00:36:50,240
[Kata mereka, pegawai kerajaan
tidak bersungguh-sungguh.]

835
00:36:51,480 --> 00:36:53,400
Malah, ada yang menjangka

836
00:36:53,400 --> 00:36:55,200
