[nyanyian ini disebar kerana]

876
00:38:32,600 --> 00:38:33,760
[kes pembunuhan Tokong Ximing]

877
00:38:33,760 --> 00:38:34,680
[belum diselesai.]

878
00:38:35,080 --> 00:38:36,840
[Jika Jabatan Pengawal Diraja
