879
00:38:37,400 --> 00:38:38,520
apa kata kita terus

880
00:38:38,520 --> 00:38:39,720
mengadakan upacara
untuk menghilangkan roh?

881
00:38:39,720 --> 00:38:40,560
Mungkin ia lebih berkesan.

882
00:38:41,080 --> 00:38:42,680
Dengan kebijaksanaan Yang Amat Berbahagia,

883
00:38:42,720 --> 00:38:43,560
pastinya tak perlu ambil peduli

884
00:38:43,560 --> 00:38:45,240
[kata-kata yang bodoh.]

885
00:38:53,880 --> 00:38:54,800
Ketua Shen,

886
00:38:55,520 --> 00:38:56,640
[adakah tuan tertinggal benda ini?]

887
00:39:09,480 --> 00:39:11,280
Pengawal istana menangkap patik
dengan tiba-tiba.

888
00:39:11,800 --> 00:39:13,360
